author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Bendigo And Adelaide Bank Says HY‍ Net Profit After Tax Attributable $231.7 Mln​
text:
Feb 12 (Reuters) - Bendigo And Adelaide Bank Ltd:
* HY ‍ NET PROFIT AFTER TAX ATTRIBUTABLE TO OWNERS OF COMPANY UP 10.9 PERCENT TO $231.7 MILLION​
* HY CASH EARNINGS ATTRIBUTABLE UP 10.7 PERCENT TO $225.3 MILLION
* ‍INTERIM DIVIDEND OF 35.0 CENTS - FULLY FRANKED ​ * HY NET INTEREST INCOME (STATUTORY) $657.7 MILLION, UP 10.4 PERCENT Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
